Create<T>(T)

Creates representer from a provider, which provides instrument and quantity at the same time. It is a shortest notation of creating a representer: you need to provide only one parameter

Examples

Creating a representer via constructor :

new QuantityRepresenter(_order.Instrument, _order.Quantity);

Creating the same representer via this method:

QuantityRepresenter.Create(_order);
